originalText: Ye don' wanna mess wit' 'im - Razor, mate. Dat one clod dat was hittin' on one of 'is girls los' 'is finger fer it, ha-ha.
If ye gunna die, die jettin'. Razor - respec'.
Ye gotta respect d' Black Sea, or else it's gunna pull ye under, mate. ::Nods.::
So Todd's been livin' down under all by 'imself? By 'd sea!
D' expedition's finally been sen' under.

Is it true ye beat D' Flinger in a flin' off? Dam'...
Never let yer feet dip in the water when jettin'. Dat's how ye lose 'em.

An' stay away, Aegis Inbastardated. Ha!

Dem torpedoes are still good to go, mate. ::Grins.::

If only she could still sail. We'd be unstoppable.

Hey, our mates've gone down into d' lighthouse.
Dam', dis place's creepin' me out.

Yea! D' Jetter's are raidin' again.
Hate 'em Black Eel clods. Dey crampin' our piracy, mate.

Seen any ghosts in d' hospital?
Wha's dat about statues comin' to life?
Dem ruins gotta be full o' loot. But no one can bloody open 'em.
